{"data": [{"id": "4745458", "title": "Descartes: The Quiet Canadian Compounder - Why Descartes Remains My Top Software Pick", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Global Communication Network (World Map Credits To Nasa)\" data-id=\"1329183101\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction </strong></h2> <p>Descartes Systems (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DSGX\" title=\"The Descartes Systems Group Inc.\">DSGX</a></span>) was the first company I covered here on Seeking Alpha. Interestingly, it was also the first stock I pitched to my Boss a few years ago during my time as a Fund Manager Assistant at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745458-descartes-quiet-canadian-compounder-my-top-software-pick-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:06:36"}, {"id": "4745469", "title": "Q3 GDP Third Estimate: Real GDP At 3.1%, Above Forecast", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gross domestic product or GDP. Business, economy, trade, Consumption, and Investment. An arrow sign pointing downwards and up in a wooden block\" data-id=\"1496930327\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Khanchit Khirisutchalual</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>The U.S. economy grew above expectations during the third quarter of this year. Real gross domestic product increased at an annual rate of 3.1% in Q3 2024, according to the third estimate. The latest estimate is above the forecasted</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745469-q3-gdp-third-estimate-real-gdp-at-3-1-percent-above-forecast", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:00:00"}, {"id": "4745463", "title": "U.S. Fed Cuts Rates By 25 Bps, Signals Fewer Cuts In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage sign\" data-id=\"1692418614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The U.S. Federal Reserve has lowered its overnight rate by another 25 basis points to 4.5%. Hafiz Noordin, Vice President &amp; Director, Active Fixed Income Portfolio Management at TD Asset Management, speaks with MoneyTalk\u2019s Anthony Okolie about the decision and why policymakers are suggesting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745463-us-fed-cuts-rates-by-25-bps-signals-fewer-cuts-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:45:00"}, {"id": "4745464", "title": "Scholastic Corporation 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Scholastic Corporation in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106255\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745464-scholastic-corporation-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:38:21"}, {"id": "4745454", "title": "Nvidia's Sellers May Be Missing The Big Picture", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia World Headquarters\" data-id=\"502379459\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.co