usiness Planning\" data-id=\"175599141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackred</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <h2><strong>FOMC Reaction and Implications</strong></h2> <p>Yesterday\u2019s significant selloff was inspired by the Fed shifting to a hawkish outlook for 2025. They now plan for only two small rate cuts totaling 0.5% during the year.</p> <p>This change</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745460-stagflation-fears-and-soaring-us-yields-s-and-p-500-next-move", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:20:00"}, {"id": "4745461", "title": "FactSet Research Systems Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by FactSet Research Systems Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106254\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745461-factset-research-systems-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:10:26"}, {"id": "4745450", "title": "Procter & Gamble: Inventory Does Not Lie And Points To Hold", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"pinocchio superliar\" data-id=\"157198425\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1202px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">THEPALMER</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>PG Stock: Previous Thesis and 2025 FYQ1 Recap</h2> <p>I last analyzed <strong>Procter &amp; Gamble</strong> stock (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PG#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PG#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">PG</a>) back in October 2024. More specifically, I published an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> on 10-5-2024 under the title of \"Procter &amp; Gamble: Buy The Dip\u201d on Seeking Alpha. As you</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745450-procter-and-gamble-inventory-does-not-lie-and-points-to-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:52:51"}, {"id": "4745456", "title": "The Yen Weakens As The BoJ Holds", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up image of Japanese Yen on a white background\" data-id=\"109835538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">gaffera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Min Joo Kang, Senior Economist, South Korea and Japan and Chris Turner, Global Head of Markets and Regional Head of Research for UK &amp; CEE</em></p> <p></p> <h2>A January hike is not a done deal, says Ueda</h2> <p>According to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745456-yen-weakens-as-boj-holds", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:50:00"}, {"id": "4745451", "title": "Super Micro Computer's Outlook Is Now A PIPE Dream", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fortunes Lost: Winning Lottery Destroyed by Spill\" data-id=\"157501967\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Saturated/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>GenAI has created incredible opportunities for companies to globally benefit from surging productivity gains and unlocking efficiency. As a result, organizations have demonstrated strong ambitions in investing in and upgrading their technology infrastructure to support</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745451-super-micro-computer-smci-outlook-is-now-a-pipe-dream", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:15:59"}]}